data: This port is still under development. If you find any problems, you can write about them.
At the moment, this part of the game has not been recreated. Stay tuned for future updates.
But that doesn't mean this is the end...
The author of this port does not take his right to the game, and does not pass it off as his game.
If something the creator of the original does not like, you can try to contact me
